description:
&lt;p&gt;Are you passionate in providing high standards of care? Would you like to make a real difference? If so then come and join our team here at Clifton Hospital. We have a position for a Ward Manager on Ward 4 which is our Nurse Therapy Led Ward. We predominantly care for patients who require rehabilitation or complex discharge planning. We fully support a multi-disciplinary team approach and work together to ensure our patients receive the highest standards of care and they have a safe and effective discharge. Your role will be pivotal in leading the team to drive forward these standards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Clifton Hospital is a community hospital of a team who are supportive of one another and has the patient at the centre of everything we do.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameCourtney BickerdikeJob titleClinical MatronEmail addresscourtney.bickerdike@nhs.netTelephone number01253 957093&lt;/p&gt;
